{
  "stem": "14387.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Most of the Norwegian Jews were businessmen-- had had their own prosperous businesses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here they were in Stockholm with no way of making a living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so they wanted to go back, which is the most idiotic, most foolish thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It seems to me that I was the only person that didn't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There may have been a reason for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One reason for that may have been that-- remember, I was British-born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My roots were not actually in Norway, and I had no family in Norway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had no personal family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You see, these refugees were mostly people who had left mothers and fathers and family behind in Norway, and they were terribly anxious for their family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe that's the reason why I was the only person who didn't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were so naive, they thought the Germans would not disturb them, and a lot of them went back-- including my husband's own family.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So in the end, it was just me and my husband left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband was a very adventurous type of person, always was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] an adventurer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went to Germany before he was married, he went to England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he said, no, if I didn't want to go back, he wouldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a son born in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that he was not going to go back with me-- without me-- and there was no way that I was going to go back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So unfortunately, my husband's family returned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, well, we all know what happened to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them escaped again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them escaped again by skiing across the border the second time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
